# Keep Vercel focused on the Flask app (app.py) + frontend + shared core.
# The Azure backend also defines an `app` variable, which would give Vercel's
# Python entrypoint detector a second candidate. Exclude it and other
# non-Vercel files so app.py is the single, unambiguous entrypoint.
azure_api/
.github/
staticwebapp.config.json
README.md
